{
  "stem": "14867.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were working, and as we were taking apart, it was heartbreaking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found all kinds of little notes saying goodbye to certain people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some-- some-- some jackets had blood all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some said-- it told us very briefly, I-- I am getting-- I'll be killed in a minute, and I'll never see you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we started to realize what is happening, what-- what is going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't certainly easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyway, so then--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then one day-- [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would announce officially on the radio that today, Jews between the age of 17 and 25, please be sure to stay outside.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You'll be picked up for work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they will say, women from 40 to 45 we need for a certain job.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they never came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But of course, everybody was so preoccupied with yourself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then one day, when they came with an announcement and said, women-- my mother was about 42-- women will be taken from the age of 40 to 50, whatever it is, will be taken to work.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister-- we were working together, and this was quite close to where we lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't tell you yet where we were living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my sister started to run home and find out where Mother is.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
